<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>NIHNAK LE TAHNAK KHATTELEI AH CH419</title>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nihnak le tahnak khat-telei ah, A tu zau in ka phan cang lai, Ihnak le
 hlauhnak khat-telei ah, Cinnak le hlehnak khat-telei ah, Atu zau in ka
 phan cang lai.

[C1]
   Na dawtmi umnak ca ah, Na serinn tha chung ka phakter, Bawipa.

[V2]
 Parnak le uainak khat-telei ah, Atu zau ah ka phan cang lai; Ceunak le
 muihnak khat-telei ah, Ruahchan le thin-phannak ralchan ah, Atu zau in ka
 tlung lai ta.

[C2]
   Na dawtmi umnak ca ah, Na serinn tha chung ka phakter, Bawipa.

[V3]
 Khua-sihnak le khua-lumnak va ral, Atu zau in ka phak lai ta; Fing le
 tlang tiva ral khat lei ah, A zungzal nunnak khua tha chungah, A tu zauah
 ka phan lai ta.

[C3]
   Na dawtmi umnak ca ah, Na serinn tha chung ka phakter, Bawipa.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>419</hymn_number>
</song>